title: Splatterhouse Xbox 360 Beta - June Build
description: This is the June 2010 build of Splatterhouse. While the game was heavily modified from it's finished version, it's still very different from the final. Also very unfinished and prone to crashing and other bugs. The XeX files will only function on an Xbox Devkit or an Xbox 360 re-flashed to function as a DevKit. Your milage may vary, released for archival purposes.
